org.pikater.web.vaadin

Class ManageUserUploads

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pikater.web.vaadin.ManageUserUploads
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, IFileUploadEvents

    public class ManageUserUploads
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, IFileUploadEvents
    A class wrapping multi file-upload functionality for a single user - an instance of this class is exclusively mapped to a particular session. This allows easy integration and nice usage of the MultiFileUpload add-on.
    See Also:
